race.comment: RECLINER KING (4) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish third (19.50) at Muswellbrook in a Mix 2/3 over 336m. One of the contenders. DUSTED OVER (3) ran below best last time finishing seventh (18.57) over 300m at this track from Box 5. Cannot be taken lightly. SEA SURGE (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (18.42) in a Grade 5 at this track. Should be thereabouts. SEVEN SUMMERS (2) looks a chance coming off a three months layoff.
